long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Multimedia Search is a default search engine dedicated to searching multimedia files. This extension is purpose-built to simplify and expedite the search process for multimedia files using straightforward commands. It is designed to cater specifically to power users and avid multimedia seekers who frequently search for images, videos, audio files, and other multimedia content online.

Learn More: https://multimediasearchapp.com
